'''默克尔细胞'''（英文：Merkel Cell），又称'''默克尔-兰维尔细胞'''（Merkel-Ranvier cell）或'''触觉上皮细胞'''（tactile epithelial cell），是一种椭圆型的[[力學感受器|力学感受器]]，对轻微碰触敏感，存在于[[脊椎动物|脊椎动物]]的[[皮肤|皮肤]]内<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=What is a Merkel Cell?|url=https://merkelcell.org/about-mcc/what-is-a-merkel-cell/|accessdate=2021-02-21|work=Merkel Cell Carcinoma|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126182154/https://merkelcell.org/about-mcc/what-is-a-merkel-cell/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Merkel cells: A review on role of merkel cells in histology and disease|url=https://www.ijofr.org/article.asp?issn=2589-5354;year=2017;volume=2;issue=2;spage=45;epage=47;aulast=Ashok#:~:text=Merkel%20cells%20(MCs),%20otherwise,receptors%20through%20the%20tactile%20meniscus.|accessdate=2021-02-21|last=Ashok|work=www.ijofr.org|archive-date=2021-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420190948/https://www.ijofr.org/article.asp?issn=2589-5354;year=2017;volume=2;issue=2;spage=45;epage=47;aulast=Ashok#:~:text=Merkel%20cells%20(MCs),%20otherwise,receptors%20through%20the%20tactile%20meniscus.|dead-url=no}}</ref>。默克尔细胞常与[[神经末梢|感觉神经末梢]]并置，形成[[默克尔神经末梢|默克尔神经末梢]]（又称默克尔细胞-[[神经突|神经突]]复合体）<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Merkel cells and neurons keep in touch|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4312710/|last=Woo|first=Seung-Hyun|last2=Lumpkin|first2=Ellen A.|date=2015-2|journal=Trends in cell biology|issue=2|doi=10.1016/j.tcb.2014.10.003|volume=25|pages=74–81|issn=0962-8924|pmc=4312710|pmid=25480024|last3=Patapoutian|first3=Ardem}}</ref>。在人体的指尖上，默克尔细胞分布广泛，与[[传入神经纤维|传入神经纤维]]的[[突触|突触]]接触<ref name=":0" />。

尽管默克尔细胞常被认为起源于[[神经嵴|神经嵴细胞]]，但最新的[[哺乳动物|哺乳动物]]试验表明，它们事实上源于[[上皮组织|上皮组织]]<ref name="BaumannHalata2003">{{cite book|author1=K. I. Baumann|author2=Zdenek Halata|author3=I. Moll|title=The Merkel cell: structure-development-function- cancerogenesis|url=https://archive.org/details/springer_10.1007-978-3-662-10358-6|accessdate=2010-05-02|year=2003|publisher=Springer|isbn=978-3-540-00374-8|pages=[https://archive.org/details/springer_10.1007-978-3-662-10358-6/page/n109 99]–}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Mammalian Merkel cells are descended from the epidermal lineage.|last=Morrison|first=Kristin|journal=Developmental Biology|issue=1|doi=10.1016/j.ydbio.2009.09.032|year=2009|volume=336|pages=76–83|pmc=2783667|pmid=19782676|author3=Ellen A. Lumpkin|author4=Stephen M. Maricich|author2=George R. Miesegaes}}</ref>。默克尔-兰维尔细胞以[[德国|德国]]科学家[[弗里德里希·西格蒙德·默克尔|弗里德里希·西格蒙德·默克尔]]、[[法国|法国]]科学家[[路易斯·安托万·兰维尔|路易斯·安托万·兰维尔]]的名字命名<ref name=":0" />。

